data.description: SELLER IS OFFERING $5,000 IN CONCESSIONS WITH A FULL PRICE OFFER TO HELP WITH RATE BUY-DOWN AND CLOSING COSTS. Come see this beautiful 4bed 2bath home located in Pecan Creek South! Property includes an incredibly functional floor plan with a sleek kitchen, matching appliances, and breakfast bar. The flooring consists of tile in wet areas and BRAND NEW carpet in living room and bedrooms, all of which is  also freshly painted. Outside you will find a MASSIVE covered patio draped with stunning vines and mature landscaping throughout, making this backyard ideal for relaxation and/or entertainment for all.
